Package StudentInfo

Class Student

java.lang.Object
StudentInfo.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Student is an entity class which stores all the information of a student.

Each student has 9 pieces of informations in total, as described below:

key: Uniquely identifies a student

firstName, lastName, matricNum, gender, nationality, age, email

accessPeriod: The period of time that the student is allowed to access MySTARS

Aaron Tay Han Yen
